<!-- Timeline Item 5 -->
<div class="timeline-item relative pl-8 mb-12">
<div class="absolute left-0 top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-orange-500 border-4 border-yellow-300 glow"></div>
<div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md card-hover transition duration-300">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center mb-4">
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text flex-1">5. Ekosistem DeFi dan DAO</h3>
<span class="bg-orange-500 text-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mt-2 md:mt-0">2020-Sekarang</span>
</div>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="bg-gray-700 p-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-600 transition">
<div class="flex items-center mb-2">
<i class="fas fa-wallet text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
<p class="font-bold text-orange-400">Decentralized Finance (DeFi)</p>
</div>
<p>Sistem keuangan alternatif yang tidak bergantung pada lembaga keuangan tradisional. Dengan menggunakan smart contract di blockchain seperti Ethereum, DeFi memungkinkan aktivitas seperti pinjam-meminjam, staking, pertukaran, dan asuransi tanpa bank.</p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3">
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-xs rounded">Lending</span>
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-xs rounded">DEX</span>
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-xs rounded">Yield Farming</span>
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-xs rounded">Stablecoins</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-gray-700 p-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-600 transition">
<div class="flex items-center mb-2">
<i class="fas fa-users text-blue-500 mr-2"></i>
<p class="font-bold text-orange-400">DAO</p>
</div>
<p>Decentralized Autonomous Organization adalah organisasi digital yang dijalankan oleh kode, bukan oleh struktur organisasi tradisional. DAO mengubah cara komunitas online mengambil keputusan bersama, berdasarkan suara pemilik token.</p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3">
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-xs rounded">Governance</span>
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-xs rounded">Voting</span>
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-xs rounded">Treasury</span>
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-xs rounded">Proposals</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
